                  <strong>UPI ID:</strong> 00000000000@ybl<br/> ```REPLACE UPI ID ```
                  <strong>Amount:</strong> â‚¹${charge}<br/>
                  <em>Use any UPI app to scan or enter the UPI ID to pay.</em>
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="footer">
                Thank you for using Smart Parking. Have a safe journey!
